<p style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 35px; color: #1c3f94;">Dear {{lead.First Name:default=Friend}},</p>
<p style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; color: #1c3f94;">Thank you for requesting your free solar consultation through the Mass Solar Connect program.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">One of our solar experts will contact you within the next 48 hours to follow up on your request for a no obligation home solar site assessment. To get a jump start, gather your past 12 months of electricity usage (in kilowatt-hours) from your utility provider.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px;">There has never been a better time to go solar. Direct Energy Solar offers cash purchase, monthly payment, and purchase financing options&mdash;we have an option to meet your specific needs. We hope to have the opportunity to help you go solar.</p>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
<p style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 0px; color: #1c3f94;">Let Direct Energy Solar help you understand your solar options. Download your free guide!</p>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="634" align="center" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
