<tr>
<td style="vertical-align: top;" width="294">
<div style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img src="http://pages.directenergysolar.com/rs/astrumsolarinc/images/UnderstandingSolarPower_Cover.jpg" border="0" alt="Your Guide to Understanding Solar Power" width="263" height="185" /></div>
</td>
<td style="vertical-align: top;" width="340">
<div style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #666666; font-weight: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;">We&rsquo;re pleased to offer you our downloadable guide which will help you better understand the benefits of going solar, financing options available, and the factors that influence the amount of your financial return. Plus, much more!</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;"><a style="font-size: 15px; color: #61af3f; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;" href="http://pages.directenergysolar.com/rs/astrumsolarinc/images/DirectEnergySolar_UnderstandingSolarPower.pdf">Download your free copy of &ldquo;Your Guide to Understanding Solar Power.&rdquo;</a></p>
