<p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px;">Thousands of Direct Energy Solar customers are harnessing the sun&rsquo;s full potential for their homes and saving money on electricity. <a style="font-size: 15px; color: #61af3f; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.directenergysolar.com/customer-stories/">Read their stories.</a></p>
